    <title>Events | Riget Zoo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Style.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <section class="animals-section">
            <h1>Events at Riget Zoo</h1>
            <p>Come and see our amazing events this year! There's something for everyone, from educational experiences to exciting shows. Don’t miss out!</p>
        </section>

        <section class="highlighted-events">
            <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Penguin Parade:</strong> Every Saturday at 2 PM. Watch our adorable penguins waddle in a fun parade for all ages.</li>
                <li><strong>Night Safari:</strong> Explore the zoo after dark every Friday and Saturday evening. Advance booking required.</li>
                <li><strong>Keeper Talks:</strong> Daily sessions at various animal enclosures. Check the schedule on your visit for timings.</li>
                <li><strong>Animal Feeding Times:</strong> Witness feeding sessions and learn about the animals’ diets and behaviors.</li>
                <li><strong>Seasonal Festivals:</strong> Join us for our Halloween Spooktacular or Winter Wonderland events. Dates to be announced!</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
